{"tid":2510250,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老+單車=馬路炸彈","createTime":"2021-04-30T04:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T11:35:26.000Z","uid":65892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"517e3556fd6b3930ef77310056e0e8c5429eb811","tid":2510250,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"今朝有件廢老係馬路中間慢行，咁我都怕左佢，靠左慢速入緊停車場個陣，佢無啦啦扭左撞埋我架車到，仲撞到我塊右鏡彎向前<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩無刮花到架車，同埋塊鏡都無事。咁我都落車問下佢有無事了，點知佢屌返我做咩唔響安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話大佬呀，你單車行兩條行線中間已經唔啱了，你轉左都唔睇下路，會路會係咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趕住返工費事再嘈，但啲單車廢老真係好恐怖，天地任我行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206740cecfbfbb22edb084ebcc5a053cc864c177","tid":2510250,"uid":142313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"我既人生之歌 暫時 係任我行"},{"pid":"623ccaff39f01f74ccd3f3a9f2742043a3ea9a92","tid":2510250,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"想問下大家，如果件阿伯真係撞壞我塊鏡係咪要報狗？"},{"pid":"853edb7596e995b41bd7d4cbf63b0d2269645509","tid":2510250,"uid":317379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"其實靠左扒頭都係好危險 大家都有錯<br />\n如果係揸車 靠左扒頭直頭係犯法"},{"pid":"34417a23b2f99ee3ffcad65ea4dc30cfa228600c","tid":2510250,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853edb7596e995b41bd7d4cbf63b0d2269645509","tid":2510250,"uid":317379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"其實靠左扒頭都係好危險 大家都有錯<br />\n如果係揸車 靠左扒頭直頭係犯法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:35:26.000Z","msg":"我無扒頭，我一直行緊左線，係件阿伯行實線中間位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}